

External code
-------------
todataurl.js (http://code.google.com/p/todataurl-png-js/)
- canvas.toDataUrl() was only implemented in Android 3.0 and we are getting the base64 image to store in the DB here

Foreground camera (http://code.google.com/p/foreground-camera-plugin/)
- Android foreground camera utility to prevent application being knocked out of memory during photo taking
